title: 3427 York Lower Duplex, Unit B
posting_body: ['$250 off first Month if you sign a lease in the next two weeks.', 'This is a newly remodeled lower half duplex (Garden Level) house (3427 York) only 7 blocks from City Park.', 'This House is in great condition with a newly remodeled interior and brand new landscaped front and back yard.', 'We have 3D tours, Video tours and can also do live stream tours.', 'OPEN HOUSES (Flexible on other showing Days/Times)', 'every Saturday 11 am to 12 pm and Sunday 2 pm to 3 pm', 'Available Now', 'Posted price is for a two year lease, it is $100/month more if you only do a one year lease.', 'This lower half of the house has 2 bedrooms and 1 bath and is approximately 1,200 sqft spread over a nice large lot that can accommodate up to 2 cars, one for each roommate.', "What sets this apart from everything else is it's size and location.", 'It is in one of the hottest neighborhoods in Denver steps away from both City Park, Downtown and the RiNo District.', 'It also has a private 2 car detached garage and is on the same block as NOLA and across from a newly remodeled 7-11.', 'Some of the other modern upgrades/amenities include:', 'All stainless steel appliances', 'Newer washer and dryer', 'Dishwasher and garbage disposal', 'Granite Counter Tops', 'Brand New Kitchen', 'In Ceiling Lighting Throughout Entire House', 'Central Heat', 'Perks of Location:', '10 Minute walk to City Park and RiNo District', 'Russell Square Park across the Street', 'On same corner as NOLA', 'Free and Ample On-Street Parking for Guests', '6 Blocks to Light Rail to DIA in 2016', 'On the Corner of a new 7-11', 'On Corner of RTD Stop', 'Rent Includes:', 'Trash Removal', '1 Parking Spot in the 2 car Private Detached Garage with one more spot adjacent uncovered.', 'One month deposit is required.', 'Credit and background check will be conducted.', 'No smoking of any kind allowed indoors.', 'Pets welcome.', 'Please contact by either Phone at or email.', 'Thanks for Looking,']
